cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.CR, cs.NE 

This paper focuses on developing efficient and effective optimization-based adversarial attack algorithms, which are commonly studied in the fields of machine learning (cs.LG), computer vision (cs.CV), and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also discusses the security aspect of these attacks, which falls under the category of cryptography and security (cs.CR). Finally, the proposed algorithm involves optimization techniques, which are also studied in the field of neural networks (cs.NE).
